@startuml diagrama de actividades Emotion

title Adaptación Socioemocional a la Discapacidad

|User|
start
:Opens Adaptación Socioemocional test card;
:Selects an option\nRegister / Modify / Consult;

if (Option selected?) then (Consult)
  |System|
  :Fetches and displays existing results\nIAB score and interpretation\nIDB score and interpretation\nSCL-90 notes;
  |User|
  :Exits;
  stop
else (Register or Modify)
  :Enters IAB score and IDB score;
  |System|
  :Shows live interpretation per score\nIAB: Mínima / Leve / Moderada / Grave\nIDB: Mínima / Leve / Moderada / Grave;
  |User|
  :Enters SCL-90 notes (optional);
  if (Wants to save?) then (yes)
    |System|
    :Saves results;
    stop
  else (no)
    :Exits;
    stop
  endif
endif

@enduml